<title>Travel to Astana — National EOR Forum 2026</title>
<meta name="description" content="Practical travel information for the National EOR Forum 2026 in Astana, Kazakhstan — visa, flights, hotel, weather and local tips.">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@600;700&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/_shared.css">
<style>
body {
  background-image:
    radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 50% at 50% -10%, rgba(200,146,42,.07) 0%, transparent 60%);
}
.info-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 48px; }
.info-card {
  background: var(--card-bg); border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
  border-radius: var(--r); padding: 24px 22px; box-shadow: var(--shadow);
}
.info-card-icon { font-size: 1.6rem; margin-bottom: 12px; }
.info-card-title { font-weight: 700; font-size: 1rem; color: var(--white); margin-bottom: 10px; }
.info-card-body { font-size: .88rem; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.75; }
.info-card-body strong { color: var(--text); }
.info-card-body a { color: var(--gold); text-decoration: none; }
.info-card-body a:hover { color: var(--gold-light); }

.tip-list { list-style: none; }
.tip-list li {
  display: flex; gap: 12px; align-items: flex-start;
  padding: 13px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--card-border);
  font-size: .9rem; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.6;
}
.tip-list li:last-child { border-bottom: 0; }
.tip-list li strong { color: var(--text); }
.tip-icon { font-size: 1.1rem; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 2px; }

.airline-row { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 10px; margin-top: 12px; }
.airline-tag {
  background: var(--card-bg); border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
  border-radius: var(--r-sm); padding: 8px 14px;
  font-size: .86rem; color: var(--text);
}

.weather-row {
  display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3,1fr); gap: 1px;
  background: var(--gold-rule); border: 1px solid var(--gold-rule);
  border-radius: var(--r); overflow: hidden; margin-bottom: 48px;
}
.weather-cell {
  background: var(--navy); padding: 18px 14px; text-align: center;
}
.weather-month { font-size: .75rem; color: var(--text-dim); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .08em; margin-bottom: 6px; }
.weather-temp { font-family: "Playfair Display", serif; font-size: 1.6rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--gold-light); }
.weather-desc { font-size: .78rem; color: var(--text-muted); margin-top: 4px; }

@media (max-width: 640px) {
  .info-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .weather-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<script src="/_nav.js"></script>

<div class="wrap">

  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="page-eyebrow">Practical Information</div>
    <h1 class="page-title">Travelling to <span>Astana</span></h1>
    <p class="page-subtitle">Everything you need to plan your trip to Kazakhstan for the National EOR Forum, August 27–28, 2026 at the Rixos President Astana.</p>
  </section>

  <!-- VENUE -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-label">Venue</div>
    <div class="card" style="display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:24px;align-items:flex-start">
      <div style="flex:1;min-width:220px">
        <div style="font-weight:700;font-size:1.05rem;color:var(--white);margin-bottom:6px">Rixos President Astana</div>
        <div style="font-size:.9rem;color:var(--text-muted);line-height:1.8">
          📍 Kunayeva 7, Astana 010000, Kazakhstan<br>
          🌐 <a href="https://www.rixos.com/en/hotel/rixos-president-astana" target="_blank" style="color:var(--gold)">rixos.com</a><br>
          📞 +7 7172 999 000
        </div>
        <div style="margin-top:14px;font-size:.84rem;color:var(--text-dim)">5-star hotel in the heart of Astana's government district. Walking distance from the Bayterek monument and the main ministries.</div>
      </div>
      <a href="https://maps.google.com/?q=Rixos+President+Astana" target="_blank" class="btn-ghost" style="flex-shrink:0;align-self:flex-start">📍 Open in Maps →</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- VISA -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-label">Visa &amp; Entry</div>
    <div class="card">
      <ul class="tip-list">
        <li>
          <span class="tip-icon">✈️</span>
          <div><strong>Visa-free access</strong> — Citizens of 60+ countries can enter Kazakhstan visa-free for 30 days, including the EU, UK, USA, Canada, Japan, South Korea, UAE, and most CIS states. Check the full list at <a href="https://www.gov.kz" target="_blank" style="color:var(--gold)">gov.kz</a>.</div>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="tip-icon">📄</span>
          <div><strong>eVisa available</strong> — For countries not on the visa-free list, an electronic visa can be obtained at <a href="https://evisa.mfa.gov.kz" target="_blank" style="color:var(--gold)">evisa.mfa.gov.kz</a>. Processing time is typically 3–5 business days. Cost: USD 25–60.</div>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="tip-icon">🛂</span>
          <div><strong>Registration</strong> — Foreign nationals must register within 3 working days of arrival. Hotels register guests automatically. If staying privately, register at the local migration service office.</div>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="tip-icon">🩺</span>
          <div><strong>Health requirements</strong> — No vaccinations currently required. Travel insurance with medical coverage is strongly recommended.</div>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="tip-icon">⚠️</span>
          <div><strong>Check early</strong> — Visa requirements can change. Always verify with the <a href="https://www.mfa.gov.kz" target="_blank" style="color:var(--gold)">Kazakhstan Ministry of Foreign Affairs</a> or your nearest Kazakhstan embassy before travelling.</div>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FLIGHTS -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-label">Getting to Astana</div>
    <div class="card">
      <div style="font-weight:700;color:var(--white);margin-bottom:8px">Nursultan Nazarbayev International Airport (NQZ)</div>
      <div style="font-size:.88rem;color:var(--text-muted);margin-bottom:16px">Located 15 km south of the city centre. Taxi to Rixos: ~20 min, ~USD 10–15.</div>
      <ul class="tip-list">
        <li><span class="tip-icon">🇰🇿</span><div><strong>Air Astana</strong> — flag carrier with direct routes from London, Frankfurt, Amsterdam, Dubai, Istanbul, Moscow, Beijing, Seoul, Delhi and many more.</div></li>
        <li><span class="tip-icon">🌍</span><div><strong>FlyArystan</strong> — low-cost subsidiary of Air Astana. Regional routes across Central Asia and Russia.</div></li>
        <li><span class="tip-icon">🔗</span><div><strong>Connections via hub cities</strong> — Almaty (TSE hub, 1h flight), Istanbul (IST), Dubai (DXB), Frankfurt (FRA), and Moscow (SVO/DME) all have strong onward connections to Astana.</div></li>
      </ul>
      <div style="margin-top:14px;font-size:.84rem;color:var(--text-dim)">Book early — August is peak summer travel season in the region. Air Astana typically releases fares 6–9 months in advance.</div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- HOTEL -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-label">Accommodation</div>
    <div class="info-grid">
      <div class="info-card">
        <div class="info-card-icon">🏨</div>
        <div class="info-card-title">Rixos President Astana (venue)</div>
        <div class="info-card-body">
          The forum venue. <strong>Book directly</strong> via <a href="https://www.rixos.com" target="_blank">rixos.com</a> and mention the EOR Forum 2026 for potential group rates.<br><br>
          <strong>Rate:</strong> ~USD 180–250/night (estimate)
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="info-card">
        <div class="info-card-icon">🏩</div>
        <div class="info-card-title">Nearby alternatives</div>
        <div class="info-card-body">
          <strong>Hilton Astana</strong> — 5★, 10 min walk<br>
          <strong>Marriott Astana</strong> — 5★, 12 min walk<br>
          <strong>InterContinental Astana</strong> — 5★, 8 min walk<br>
          <strong>Hotel Kazakhstan Astana</strong> — 4★, budget-friendly<br><br>
          All within 1–2 km of the venue.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <div style="font-size:.86rem;color:var(--text-muted)">💡 <strong style="color:var(--text)">Book accommodation early.</strong> Astana hosts numerous government and industry events in August. Hotel availability fills up quickly, especially at 5-star properties near the government district.</div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WEATHER -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-label">Weather in August</div>
    <div class="weather-row">
      <div class="weather-cell"><div class="weather-month">Average high</div><div class="weather-temp">29°C</div><div class="weather-desc">Warm &amp; sunny</div></div>
      <div class="weather-cell"><div class="weather-month">Average low</div><div class="weather-temp">15°C</div><div class="weather-desc">Cool evenings</div></div>
      <div class="weather-cell"><div class="weather-month">Humidity</div><div class="weather-temp">Low</div><div class="weather-desc">Dry continental</div></div>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <ul class="tip-list">
        <li><span class="tip-icon">☀️</span><div>August is one of Astana's best months — long sunny days (16h daylight), low humidity, minimal rain. Light summer clothing is fine during the day.</div></li>
        <li><span class="tip-icon">🧥</span><div>Evenings can drop to 12–15°C. Bring a light jacket for outdoor evenings and for heavily air-conditioned conference rooms.</div></li>
        <li><span class="tip-icon">🌬️</span><div>Astana is known for wind. A windbreaker is useful if you plan to explore the city on foot.</div></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- LOCAL TIPS -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-label">Local tips</div>
    <div class="card">
      <ul class="tip-list">
        <li><span class="tip-icon">💱</span><div><strong>Currency:</strong> Kazakhstani Tenge (KZT). ~1 USD ≈ 460 KZT (check current rate). ATMs widely available. Major hotels accept USD/EUR/cards. Exchange at airport or banks for best rates — street exchangers should be avoided.</div></li>
        <li><span class="tip-icon">📱</span><div><strong>SIM card:</strong> Buy a local SIM on arrival at the airport (Kcell, Beeline, Tele2). Data is cheap — ~1 USD for several GB. Your phone must be unlocked.</div></li>
        <li><span class="tip-icon">🚕</span><div><strong>Transport:</strong> Yandex Go (Yandex Taxi) works well and is inexpensive. Uber is also available. Metered taxis from the street are fine too — agree the price before getting in.</div></li>
        <li><span class="tip-icon">🕐</span><div><strong>Time zone:</strong> Astana is UTC+5 (no daylight saving). Plan your calls and connections accordingly.</div></li>
        <li><span class="tip-icon">🗣</span><div><strong>Language:</strong> Kazakh and Russian are official languages. English is spoken at most hotels and the conference venue. Google Translate works well offline for Kazakh and Russian.</div></li>
        <li><span class="tip-icon">🍽</span><div><strong>Food:</strong> Astana has excellent Central Asian cuisine — try beshbarmak (meat and noodles) and samsa (baked pastries). The EXPO area and government district have good international restaurants. Hotel restaurants are reliable but pricey.</div></li>
        <li><span class="tip-icon">🏛</span><div><strong>Worth visiting:</strong> Bayterek tower (iconic landmark, 5 min from venue), the Palace of Peace and Reconciliation (pyramid), Khan Shatyr entertainment centre, and the futuristic EXPO 2017 district. Astana's architecture is genuinely spectacular.</div></li>
        <li><span class="tip-icon">🔌</span><div><strong>Power:</strong> Type C/F plugs, 220V/50Hz. European adapters work fine. Bring a universal adapter if coming from the UK, US or Asia.</div></li>
        <li><span class="tip-icon">💊</span><div><strong>Pharmacy:</strong> Well-stocked pharmacies throughout the city. Basic medications widely available without prescription.</div></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <div class="card" style="text-align:center;padding:36px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--navy-light),rgba(200,146,42,.1))">
    <div style="font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:1.3rem;color:var(--white);margin-bottom:8px">Ready to join us in Astana?</div>
    <div style="font-size:.9rem;color:var(--text-muted);margin-bottom:20px">Register now to secure your place at Kazakhstan's national EOR Forum.</div>
    <a href="/register" class="btn-gold">Register →</a>
  </div>

</div>

